<h1> Learn To Hack </h1>

<h2>A short guide! (For legal reasons, not really.)</h2>

<button class="accordion">What is considered a successful "hack"?</button>
<div class="panel">
  <p>A successful hack, in most modern systems, is gaining a remote shell access with Sudo. A remote shell allows the hacker to execute commands, and Sudo allows them to act as an administrator. The easiest way to do this is open a port on the server and connect to it. <p>
  <div class="center"> 
  <img src="Sudo.png" alt="Manual page for Sudo" width="800" height="auto"> 
  </div>
</div>

